fill up a name over here, the email, the phone number, you can hit submit or you can collapse

00:01:25.559 --> 00:01:31.680
it and then you can separate it in different chunks and so user can actually focus on where

00:01:31.680 --> 00:01:32.680
they are filling.

00:01:32.680 --> 00:01:38.760
To make it even a step above, a little more professional, a little more classy, what we

