accordion what we do is the same way you would do an accordion but we end up actually

00:01:58.279 --> 00:02:03.680
maximizing the usage of our accordion panel so we can actually have icons which says like

00:02:03.680 --> 00:02:07.480
hey which are the accordion panels that need attention from the user.

00:02:07.480 --> 00:02:12.880
In this case I have an exclamation mark with red which says hey these sections are supposed

