00:02:24.199 --> 00:02:31.759
panel which the new title and the title is the information they ended up filling up and

00:02:31.759 --> 00:02:38.720
then I also update the icon which is a green checkmark so in a way I just first glance

00:02:38.720 --> 00:02:42.440
they know this is the information they filled up so if they want to go back and update it

00:02:42.440 --> 00:02:43.440
